[man over P.A.] <i> Miss Garland</i>
    <i> to the stage, please.</i>

01:28:11.320 --> 01:28:13.353
<i> Miss Garland to the stage.</i>

01:28:19.728 --> 01:28:22.462
<i> Miss Garland to the stage,</i>
