01:28:24.767 --> 01:28:25.966
<i> Miss Garland.</i>

01:28:27.936 --> 01:28:29.703
<i> You're late, Miss Garland.</i>

01:28:30.606 --> 01:28:33.940
<i> Miss Garland,</i>
<i>you should be on stage, please.</i>

