I'm here.

01:29:13.115 --> 01:29:15.849
Hey, there's a lady up here.

01:29:17.920 --> 01:29:19.686
London, I love you.

01:29:21.023 --> 01:29:23.123
It's true, it's true.

01:29:23.525 --> 01:29:25.659
-Of all the towns I've loved...
     -[man] Get off the...

01:29:25.661 --> 01:29:27.394
...I love London best.

