[singing out of tune]
      <i> ¶ San Francisco ¶</i>

01:29:32.401 --> 01:29:34.634
<i> ¶ Open your Golden Gate ¶</i>

01:29:34.770 --> 01:29:37.971
<i> ¶ You'll let nobody wait</i>
     <i> Outside your door ¶</i>

